snippet.title: Sinister Halloween New Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience a Halloween night in Mountain peaks, Northern Canada.
Famous for its Horror Festival. You go out with your friends, trick or treating, entering haunted themed houses as you make your way to the big party, but this year's holiday of the afterlife brings something sinister.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/747690/Sinister_Halloween/
#halloween #scarygame #horrorgame #vr
